Well, I didn't have any credit.
嗯，我没有话费了。

186
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:42,200
No wonder.
难怪。

187
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,720
That means, oh, now I understand.
意思是，哦，现在我明白了。

188
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,720
No wonder.
难怪。

189
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,720
Exactly.
没错。

190
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:51,920
It's a great phrase to start off your sentence by explaining or letting the other person
这是一个很棒的短语，可以用它来开始你的句子，解释或让对方

191
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:58,000
know that you finally understand why this happened or you understand what the situation
知道你终于明白为什么发生这件事，或者你理解了当时的情况

192
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,000
was.
是怎样的。

193
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:08,280
