Well, that's usually teenagers.
嗯，那通常是青少年。

211
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:47,640
Yeah, I don't send 100 messages a day.
是啊，我一天不发100条消息。

212
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:49,800
I mostly use messages.
我主要用消息。

213
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:52,320
I don't call people very often.
我不经常打电话。

214
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:56,880
