00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:23,520
did send, I don't know, 100, 200 messages a day because it was that new way of communicating
一天发，我不知道，100、200条消息，因为那是与人交流的新方式

221
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:24,520
with people.
。

