So for example, instead of writing skate, like skateboard, they would write S-K and
比如，不写skate，像滑板，他们会写S-K和

237
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,380
then the number eight.
数字8。

238
00:11:31,380 --> 00:11:32,380
So skate.
所以是skate。

239
00:11:32,380 --> 00:11:33,380
That's right.
没错。

240
00:11:33,380 --> 00:11:34,380
Skate.
Skate。

241
00:11:34,380 --> 00:11:35,380
Skate.
滑冰。

242
00:11:35,380 --> 00:11:36,380
It's so strange.
这太奇怪了。

243
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:39,520
